It would be helpful to have more info on the issue. Are you using a RoboRIO 2.0? If so, have you imaged it yet? Are you connected to the RoboRIO with a USB A to B or some other way? How is it powered? These would be nice to know so we can help out more.

I had a problem when I was setting the team number (using the software you’re using in the screenshot) where I couldn’t see the RoboRIO either, and I had to click on the Format Target button on the right hand side and then click rescan once or twice in order to see the RoboRIO.

The documentation for imaging a RoboRIO 2.0 is here: Link to RoboRIO 2.0

If you need documentation for imaging the RoboRIO 1.0, click on the link within the site above. It should be at the top of the page.

Let us know how we can help more!
